  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink68-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">parattai tāṉ talaimakaḷaip puṟaṅkūṟi vaittut taṉṉait talaimakaḷ
          puṟaṅkūṟiṉāḷākap piṟarkkuk kūṟiṉamai kēṭṭa talaivi talaimakaṟkuc colliyatu.
        </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink68">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l>kaṉṉi viṭiyaṟ kaṇaikkā lāmpa</l>
          <l>ṟāmarai pōla malaru mūra</l>
          <l>pēṇā ḷōniṉ peṇṭē</l>
          <l>yānta ṉaṭakkavun tāṉaṭaṅ kalaḷē.</l>
        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

          <l> O man from a village! </l>
          <l rend="indent4"> Where the hollow-stalked white lotus</l>
          <l rend="indent6"> blooms like the red lotus at early dawn – </l>
          <l> Has your woman no respect? </l>
          <l> </l>
          <p/>
          <l> Although we dog her steps, she does not yield. </l>

        </lg>


      </div>
    </body>
